title: Incredibly well maintained townhome!  two pools, tennis, basketball!
posting_body: ['Incredibly well maintained townhome!', 'The Capri model is a favorite featuring 2 bedrooms with vaulted ceilings, 2 full walk-in closets for the main bedroom, a similarly sized 2nd bedroom with a large walk in closet, 2nd bathroom that is larger than other models, and a 1/2 bath downstairs!', 'This home has volume ceilings downstairs and open floor plan living.', 'The space in this model is very smartly designed.', 'Located in the heart of the luxury Lyons Road gated communities & the best of Palm Beach County.', 'Zoned for A rated schools including charter schools BridgePrep Academy then Somerset Canyons Middle & High School.', 'Community offers staffed gated security, two pools, tennis, basketball, fitness center, & clubhouse.', 'Credit score of 650 and credit check is not flexible.', 'Small pet considered.', 'Contact us to schedule a tour today.', 'Please TEXT me your NAME and', 'AD REFERENCE', 'below and We will contact you ASAP.', 'Book your appointment online today!', 'ANNUAL RENTALS ONLY.', 'Ad Reference:', 'RX10810540', 'Text at:', 'show contact info', 'Ask for ANDREW', 'Availability can change daily, If this rental is not available or isn’t the property for you, Text me or call me and We will help you find the right residence for you.', 'We have rentals all over Palm Beach and Broward County!']
